\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Vaseline Lip Therapy Rosy Lips .16oz Pink Tinted Lip Balm Pure Petroleum Jelly</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">14.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Vaseline Lip Therapy Rosy Lip Balm is clinically proven to help heal dry lips and leave them looking beautiful, conditioned, and naturally rosy after just one application and is suitable for everyday use.</p><p>Formulated with 100% pure triple-purified petroleum jelly, this Vaseline lip therapy lip balm works to lock in moisture and provide proven relief for dull, dry, cracked, sunburnt, windburned or damaged lips. The lip balm goes on soft and lightweight while providing the utmost moisturization for your lips; no greasy residue is left behind.</p><p>Featuring all the great qualities Vaseline products are known for - instant hydration, non-stick and non-greasy formula, and long-lasting quality – this mini lip balm with plastic close top is all those great features but with a little extra attention on the beauty and makeup front. Leaving a naturally pink tint on lips with a subtle rose fragrance, skip the heavy lipstick or lip gloss application that instantaneously dries out lips Instead, go for a naturally pink tinted lip that leaves lips glossy but hydrated and conditioned simultaneously.</p><p>This pocket-sized .16oz Vaseline lip balm is also a great addition to your makeup bag and travel accessories; small enough to tote with you wherever you go, take it on your next vacation, road trip, road trip or ski or snowboarding adventure. Vaseline Lip Therapy Rosy Lip Balm Moisturizer with Pure Petroleum Jelly softens and soothes dry lips for healthy, deeply moisturized, and conditioned lips - also a great addition to any survival kit or first aid bag.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-a